<item>
 <title>E você, o que compartilhas?</title>
 <link>http://mutgamb.org/blog/E-voce-o-que-compartilhas</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;F&amp;eacute;rias. &amp;Eacute;poca que as pessoas lotam lugares: parques, museus, praias e depois compartilham suas experi&amp;ecirc;ncias nas redes sociais.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paulo Bicarato achou o &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.thebiginternetmuseum.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;Grande Museu da Internet&lt;/a&gt;: n&amp;atilde;o precisa de $ para visitar e s&amp;oacute; fecha no Carnaval brasileiro. Em seu acervo online &amp;eacute; poss&amp;iacute;vel acessar narrativas (como o gif &lt;em&gt;Peanut Butter Jelly Time&lt;/em&gt;, 2000) de como a internet tornou-se o que &amp;eacute; hoje.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://www.thebiginternetmuseum.com/uploads/mediagallery/Peanut-butter-jelly-time_def.gif&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ah, a internet...essa que causa disson&amp;acirc;ncias sobre controle de fluxos, que &lt;a href=&quot;http://efeefe.no-ip.org/blog/pra-qu%C3%AA&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;levanta&lt;/a&gt; questionamentos necess&amp;aacute;rios, mas que tamb&amp;eacute;m mostra que &amp;eacute; poss&amp;iacute;vel viver muito, &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.jcom.com.br/pesquisahistorica/leitura/130448&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;al&amp;eacute;m das expectativas previstas&lt;/a&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;E conecta a&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, como a linda &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.openculture.com/2012/12/the_recycled_orchestra.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;The Recycled Orchestra&lt;/a&gt;, no Paraguai:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;281&quot; mozallowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://player.vimeo.com/video/52711779?title=0&amp;amp;byline=0&amp;amp;portrait=0&amp;amp;color=ff9933&quot; webkitallowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;420&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(...) e as bicicletas quase-l&amp;uacute;dicas feitas de papel&amp;atilde;o, pelo &lt;a href=&quot;http://blogs.estadao.com.br/homem-objeto/bicicleta-de-papelao-sera-fabricada-em-breve/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;israelense Izhar Gafni&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;rtecenter&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://blogs.estadao.com.br/homem-objeto/files/2012/12/bicicletapapelao-e1356034680399.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
